Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:29.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}And you alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:31.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}Can you hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:38.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}誰もいない線路沿いをなぞってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}大袈裟に泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:43.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}笑ってほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}鮮明でいたい思い出を抱きしめている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:55.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}さよならよりずっと大切な言葉で伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:58.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}ありふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}でも特別で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:08.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}見えなかったものが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:13.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}どうして？溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:14.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}もう一度　生まれ変わろうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:25.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}また　私はここを選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:26.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:30.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}あなたと　また巡り逢ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:36.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}もう離さない　今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}約束なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}孤独に迷う日々でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:45.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:48.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:55.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(1920,26)\fad(300,1647)\blur3}I'm whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.15,0:22:29.20,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}你还好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.20,0:22:31.99,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}听得见吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.99,0:22:38.17,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}我走在无人的铁路线上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}哭得撕心裂肺
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.00,0:22:43.71,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}盼你重拾笑容
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.59,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}细数着刻骨铭心的回忆
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.59,0:22:55.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}诉说往事的念头远胜过道别
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.89,0:22:58.69,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}他们司空见惯
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}却又独一无二
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.23,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}如果没有这双眼睛
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.23,0:23:08.20,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}曾经错过的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.20,0:23:13.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}怎会纷纷映入眼帘
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.08,0:23:14.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.12,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}如果能够再度降生于世
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.12,0:23:25.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}我还会选择这个地方吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.00,0:23:26.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.00,0:23:30.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}如果能够再度与你相逢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.97,0:23:36.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}我定然要与你朝夕相伴
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.64,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}即使未曾许下约定
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.65,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}即便每日独自惆怅
Dialogue: 1,0:23:42.65,0:23:45.65,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}纵是落泪也无妨
Dialogue: 1,0:23:45.65,0:23:48.90,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\blur3}黎明一定会到来
Dialogue: 1,0:23:48.90,0:23:55.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,1647)\blur3}我正哼着摇篮曲 愿你回家不迷路
